        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Did the vegetables get better?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Yeah! They're getting more and more lively every day."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "That's good."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x11b,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x1b,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Still, you've been getting pretty amazing lately, Sophie. You did a great job."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1a,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Ehehehehe. Really?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. Ever since Plachta showed up, your alchemy has been getting really amazing, Sophie."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Did you find some sort of secret trick?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, Plachta told me to really think about what kind of power alchemy is."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "What does that mean?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Alchemy uses wishes and desires about \"wanting to become something\"."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "It's important for alchemists to listen to the voices of materials, and then apply their own feelings to that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "A wish to become something..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. That's why lately, I've been trying to take the materials into consideration."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x44,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "...I see. Anyway, thanks again for taking care of this. This is my way of saying thanks."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1b,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Wow, thank you so much!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I'll let you know if we need anything else."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Okay! Just leave it to me!"
